videos.headline: Dillon Gabriel rockets 41-yard TD pass vs. Louisville
videos.description: Dillon. Gabriel fires a deep pass to Ryan O'Keefe who beats his defender to score a 41-yard UCF touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dillon Gabriel rockets 41-yard TD pass vs. Louisville) 2021/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Malik Cunningham leaps for Louisville TD
videos.description: Malik Cunningham gets to the outside and jumps over a defender to reach the end zone and score a 7-yard Louisville touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Malik Cunningham leaps for Louisville TD) 2021/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaylon Robinson makes unreal TD grab for UCF
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel lofts a pass to Jaylon Robinson who elevates to make an amazing catch with the defender all over him in the end zone for a 15-yard UCF touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jaylon Robinson makes unreal TD grab for UCF) 2021/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Mitchell's short TD ties the game
videos.description: Louisville ties the score at 14-14 as Jalen Mitchel takes the handoff and powers his way to a 2-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jalen Mitchell's short TD ties the game) 2021/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Malik Cunningham connects with Marshon Ford for Louisville TD
videos.description: Louisville takes a 21-14 lead over UCF as Malik Cunningham connects with Marshon Ford for a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Malik Cunningham connects with Marshon Ford for Louisville TD) 2021/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ryan O'Keefe passes to Dillon Gabriel for UCF 20-yard TD
videos.description: Ryan O'Keefe passes to Dillon Gabriel on a double pass play to score a 20-yard touchdown for UCF.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ryan O'Keefe passes to Dillon Gabriel for UCF 20-yard TD) 2021/09/17

videos.headline: Malik Cunningham fakes out the defense for short Louisville TD
videos.description: Louisville retakes the lead as Malik Cunningham uses a fake pass to fool the defense then slips his way into the end zone to score a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Malik Cunningham fakes out the defense for short Louisville TD) 2021/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dillon Gabriel throws TD dart to Brandon Johnson
videos.description: UCF fights back to tie the game at 28-28 as Dillon Gabriel fires a quick pass to Brandon Johnson for a 6-yard touchdown strike.

videos.headline: Braden Smith connects with Trevion Cooley for 45-yard Louisville TD
videos.description: Braden Smith throws a deep pass to a wide-open Trevion Cooley who waltzes into the end zone for a 45-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Braden Smith connects with Trevion Cooley for 45-yard Louisville TD) 2021/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dillon Gabriel dives through a hit for a UCF TD
videos.description: UCF ties the score at 35-35 as Dillon Gabriel dives and takes a hit to score a 6-yard touchdown late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dillon Gabriel dives through a hit for a UCF TD) 2021/09/17 ESHEET
